text: Heidi Antikatzidis (born 4 March 1977) is a Greek equestrian. She competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Greek female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Greece Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Athens
